OL,3,CThousands take on Brighton marathon
OL,5,FThousands of people are today enjoying
OL,6,Fthe final day of the Brighton Marathon
OL,7,FWeekend ` the city's annual festival
OL,8,Fof running.
OL,10,FMore than 14,000 people are scheduled
OL,11,Fto start the centrepiece event of the
OL,12,Fweekend, the Brighton Marathon, which
OL,13,Fstarts in Preston Park, threads
OL,14,Fthrough the city and then takes
OL,15,Fparticipants along the world-famous
OL,16,Fseafront, past iconic landmarks such
OL,17,Fas the Palace Pier and Brighton i360.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G1/4
