OL,3,CThousands take on Brighton marathon
OL,5,FEngland Rugby World Cup winner Jess
OL,6,FBreach was the official starter and
OL,7,Fgot the marathon participants under
OL,8,Fway.
OL,10,FDespite blustery conditions, thousands
OL,11,Fof spectators are lining the streets
OL,12,Fto cheer on those taking part
OL,13,Fincluding at community cheer zones and
OL,14,Fthe brand new Pride Promenade - a
OL,15,Fdedicated stretch of the route
OL,16,Fcelebrating the city's LGBTQIA+
OL,17,Fcommunity
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G2/4
