OL,3,CThousands take on Brighton marathon
OL,5,FOther events taking place as part of
OL,6,Fthe festival today include the
OL,7,FBrighton & Hove 10K and the first-ever
OL,8,FBrighton Trail Marathon, organised by
OL,9,FMaverick, which sees participants take
OL,10,Fon 36K of trails on the beautiful
OL,11,FSouth Downs before sharing the final
OL,12,F6K of the official Brighton Marathon
OL,13,Froute.
OL,15,FThe Brighton and Hove 10K was the
OL,16,Ffirst event to start at 08:45 this
OL,17,Fmorning with more than 3,500 people
OL,18,Ftaking part. Kieran Barnes won the
OL,19,Fmen's race in 31:33 while Josie Wren-
OL,20,FGolder was the first female finisher
OL,21,Fin 36:59.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G3/4
